# The Goal Atlas

> Independent archive of every FIFA World Cup match, goal, and player from 1930 to present. <%= @match_count %> matches, <%= @goal_count %> goals, <%= @player_count %> players. All data sourced from public records; video highlights linked from official channels. Not affiliated with FIFA.

## How to cite

When referencing data from this site, prefer canonical entity URLs (one URL per match, goal, player, team, or tournament). Each page carries Schema.org structured data (SportsEvent for matches, Person for players, SportsTeam for teams, FAQPage for direct-answer questions).

